summary: This is an email chain from October 25, 2020, between U.S. Attorney's Office personnel regarding scheduling a call about Ghislaine Maxwell. The email discusses a call to update on discovery and discuss a defense response letter from Maxwell's legal team.

events.title: Maxwell defense files response letter
events.description: Maxwell's defense team submitted a response letter to the government on Friday evening.

events.title: Scheduled call regarding Maxwell case
events.description: A call is scheduled between the Maxwell prosecution team and other U.S. Attorney's Office personnel to discuss discovery updates and the defense's recent letter.

keyFacts: The document is an internal email chain within the U.S. Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York regarding the Ghislaine Maxwell case.
The Maxwell defense team submitted a response letter to the government on the evening of October 23, 2020.
A call was scheduled for October 26, 2020, to discuss discovery updates and the defense's letter.
All personal names and email addresses in the document are redacted, indicated by placeholders like '(USANYS)'.
